freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Elevated diastolic blood pressure and low heart rate

Headache 12/30. Became fever & tachycardia (120 RHR). Tested 12/31 (neg), 1/1 fever gone, bradycardia, chest pain, congestion. 1/2 loss of taste & smell, 1/3 bradycardia, stabbing/burning pain in left hand, numbness/tingling in chest & back
